Fourth Department,

June, 1989

(June 2, 1989) Elizabeth Chase, as Executrix of Thomas Chase, Deceased, Appellant, v Jamestown Civic Auto Ramps, Inc., et al., Respondents. (And a Third-Party Action.)

Case settled and appeal dismissed without costs. (Appeal from order of Supreme Court, Chautauqua County, Cass, J.) Present — Callahan, J. P., Denman, Green, Pine and Davis, JJ.
